---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Affiliate Disclosure" description="SmashHit affiliate disclosure — how we earn commissions and how it affects our reviews.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <nav class="text-xs text-slate-500 mb-6" aria-label="Breadcrumb"><a href="/" class="hover:text-slate-800">Home</a> › <span class="text-slate-700 font-medium">Affiliate Disclosure</span></nav>
    <h1 class="font-[Barlow_Condensed] text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
    <div class="space-y-5 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
      <p>SmashHit (smashhit.in) participates in the Amazon Associates Programme (India) and the Flipkart Affiliate Programme. As an affiliate, we may earn a commission when you purchase a product through a link on this site, at no additional cost to you.</p>
      <p>Affiliate income helps us cover the cost of purchasing rackets for review, maintaining the site, and producing new content. It does not influence the products we choose to review, the scores we assign, or the recommendations we make.</p>
      <p>Links to third-party retailers are marked with an external link icon. Prices shown on this site are indicative — always check the retailer for current pricing before purchasing.</p>
      <p>This disclosure complies with the FTC's guidelines on endorsements and testimonials, and with ASCI guidelines applicable in India.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
